questions.question_text:
You have a file named Reg1.reg that contains the following content.
//IMG//

What is the effect of importing the file?

discussion.content:
Answer is Correct ;
When a member of the Guests group signs out, the entire profile is deleted. https://ss64.com/nt/syntax-security_groups.html
But if the same user was a member of the administrators their profile is not deleted.
